comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-02T09:23:42.332Z",codex-release-agent,"Duplicate check before create: ran pm context --limit 10; pm search 'release 2026.5.2 changelog telemetry migration' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20; pm get pm-x6ni; pm search 'release readiness workflow npm publish GitHub release' --limit 10. No active release item matched; prior release item pm-x6ni is closed and the latest audit lineage is pm-23me -> pm-2eb3."
  "2026-05-02T09:29:00.102Z",codex-release-agent,"Release audit finding before fix: temp previous-version compatibility passed with no tracker-data migration breakage. Telemetry stack is healthy via /healthz (queue depth 0, one consumer, 5,783 events in last 24h), but ignored private helper scripts have endpoint/payload drift. Sentry currently has 8 unresolved high-priority groups, all expected PmCliError usage/validation failures, so Sentry capture must filter expected CLI errors before release."
  "2026-05-02T10:01:30.181Z",codex-release-agent,"Release evidence: previous-version compatibility passed in /tmp/pm-release-compat-final-E1GAqT with @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.5.1-2 items read and mutated by current 2026.5.2; comments, notes, learnings, linked files/docs/tests, reminders, events, and close_reason were preserved and validate ok=true. Telemetry check: API /healthz ok, Grafana reachable, RabbitMQ pm.telemetry.events depth 0/0 with 1 consumer, Postgres 33,387 total events and 5,783 events in the last 24h. Sentry check: 8 existing unresolved groups were handled PmCliError usage/validation failures; release fix filters expected PmCliError from exception capture and adds optional Sentry release/sourcemap upload. GitHub release environment now has NPM_TOKEN and SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN configured without exposing values. Local gates passed: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile, pnpm build, pnpm typecheck, pnpm test (82 files/1089 tests), pnpm test:coverage 100%, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage 100%, pnpm version:check --verify-next, pnpm security:scan, npm pack --dry-run, pnpm smoke:npx, release notes generation, and pm test pm-5jw8 --run --progress. Validation: resolution metadata ok, normalize dry-run clean; history drift warnings remain limited to six legacy items."
